Efes Pilsen Beer Drops Turkish Team Sponsorship, Hurriyet Says

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-02-11T06:10:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/efes-pilsen-beer-drops-turkish-team-sponsorship-hurriyet-says.html
Anadolu Efes Biracilik & Malt
Sanayii AS, the brewer of Efes Pilsen beer, has withdrawn its
sponsorship of the Turkish national soccer team, complying with
new regulations on alcohol, Hurriyet newspaper said.  A friendly match against  South Korea  in the northern city
of Trabzon on Feb. 9 was the first time the national side has
appeared without the Efes Pilsen logo in nine years, the
newspaper said.  Efes has also cut its backing of 13 league clubs, including
Besiktas, Fenerbahce and Galatasaray, the newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
